                  </hi>. I am a solicitor—on 15th September, 1865, the prisoner executed this deed (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—it is dated the 12th, I attested it on the 15th—it was signed by some of the creditors before it was executed—I know a person named Edward William Perry—he was never in my service—he assisted me in going round to get signatures to the deed—I was not aware of any assignment having been made by the bankrupt in August—he did not tell me that any such transaction had taken place.</p>
